{"tid":1049052,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中国用4輪車偽裝成俄國T90戰車","createTime":"2019-03-06T04:18:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-08T11:23:31.000Z","uid":184679,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a28ed659dcfa138c6306372b363e650dd81ac395","tid":1049052,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T04:18:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2019-03-03/656/20190303002840.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2019-03-03%2F656%2F20190303002840.jpg&h=8092b02a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n這就是俄製T-90戰車，然而它的履帶並不觸地，中間其實包裹了一輛四輪車。(圖/網路) <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n防衛部落格(defence-blog)報導，這張網路照片立即引發了大量的評論，大陸軍方沒有說明這輛偽裝戰車的用述，許多網友稱讚其高明，也希望這輛T-90模型可以發揮更多戰鬥訓練的功用。<br />\n<br />\n一些專家表示，它可能是用於測試陸軍攻擊直升機、戰鬥機的偵查系統，了解系統對目標的辨識能力，它應該不是只有T-90一種偽裝，還可能模擬其他種類的戰鬥車輛。<br />\n<br />\nT-90是由烏拉爾捷爾陸戰裝備製造廠(Uralvagonzavod)於1992年推出的第三代俄羅斯主力戰車，由於前一代T-80戰車採用燃氣渦輪機昂貴又複雜，蘇聯解體後無法繼續使用高貴的戰車，於是以T-72戰車為基礎的改進型就登場了，最初稱為T-72BU，後來更名為T-90。物美價廉的表現，迅速成為俄羅斯陸軍的主要裝甲解決方案，因其具有成本效益的火力，操控性和耐用性。<br />\n<br />\nT-90取消掉裝填手，裝有自動火控系統，砲手和指揮官可以有效地分工，操作主砲、同軸機機和防空機槍。<br />\n<br />\nT-90問世後，很快獲得原俄系戰車使用國的訂單，包括阿爾及利亞、亞塞拜然、土庫曼、伊拉克、越南和委內瑞拉。然而最大的出口對象是印度，成為印度阿瓊戰車開發不順的替代方案，印度購買了620輛戰車，並計劃在當地生產1000輛。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20190303002835-260417\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinatimes.com%2Frealtimenews%2F20190303002835-260417&d=iefYBA3dMTKG%2BriJzBrQhQEDdXZq%2B7ycbDpBQOFx8Mg%3D&h=ac1c4753\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20190303002835-260417</a>"},{"pid":"b3c6c29e344656d5dcccc457596acf4c4d673edc","tid":1049052,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T04:20:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a90dbfd71b840a69b0ab59f6552779aad91e02d0","tid":1049052,"uid":60655,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T04:22:37.000Z","msg":"許多網友稱讚其高明，也希望這輛T-90模型可以發揮更多戰鬥訓練的功用。<br />\n<br />\n咁都有得兜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bd87a04ed05ae91a8106b8a981fd4edc9a57dac","tid":1049052,"uid":50328,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T04:25:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7f79f5008ed0f913c7cd377c43b4755ec39ee3b2","tid":1049052,"uid":128210,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T09:37:14.000Z","msg":"疑兵之計好正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有咩問題？"},{"pid":"34add3dd8fc1050d8e008c2fcf8cc55bf3c3393f","tid":1049052,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T10:27:31.000Z","msg":"豬扮虎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a192174fe58af56a0f3a2c47d3d8d4fce379c5e","tid":1049052,"uid":153239,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T10:36:47.000Z","msg":"它應該不是只有T-90一種偽裝，還可能模擬其他種類的戰鬥車輛。<br />\n<br />\n唔係偽裝 但可以模擬<br />\n唔是好明, 姐係真堅係有相關性能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f70fd1d463344508ca7ac988ea90885352bda59","tid":1049052,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a192174fe58af56a0f3a2c47d3d8d4fce379c5e","tid":1049052,"uid":153239,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T10:36:47.000Z","msg":"它應該不是只有T-90一種偽裝，還可能模擬其他種類的戰鬥車輛。<br />\n<br />\n唔係偽裝 但可以模擬<br />\n唔是好明, 姐係真堅係有相關性能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T11:14:50.000Z","msg":"不是只有呀"},{"pid":"c9bda1a9f63367cd8c6427dc9bb66d61a2c7995b","tid":1049052,"uid":153239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8f70fd1d463344508ca7ac988ea90885352bda59","tid":1049052,"uid":70786,"like":0,